{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/notebook/gatsby/learn/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h4 id=\"四个api文件\"><a href=\"#%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%AAapi%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"四个api文件 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>四个API文件</h4>\n<p><strong>gatsby在根目录可以配置四个文件(可选)，用来控制网页的行为和展示。</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>\n配置文件，用于启用插件，定义公共站点数据等。可以在这里配置一些全局变量，在网页中可以通过<code class=\"language-text\">GraphQL</code>获取。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-browser.js</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-node.js</code>\n该文件会在启动项目的时候运行一次，主要用于手动生成一些页面。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-ssr.js</code></li>\n</ol>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/blog/notebook/gatsby/learn/#%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%AAapi%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\">四个API文件</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby 概述","date":"2015-05-01 22:12","description":"Gatsby知识点","type":"gatsby"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/notebook/gatsby/learn/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/notebook/gatsby/markdown/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby 之 markdown文件展示"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/notebook/gatsby/question/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby问题记录"}}}}}